<div class="home-banner">
  <div class= "container">
    <div class="home-banner-text">
      <h1 class="home-banner-header">
        Do what you want to do!
      </h1>
      <p class="home-banner-explanation">
        With Joind you can find and create any Project or Activitiy with likeminded students!
      </p>
      <div class="home-banner-buttons">
        <button class="btn btn-light btn-big">
          Create!
        </button>
        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-standard btn-big">
          Find!
        </button>
      </div> 
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="section-instruction-cards">
  <div class="container d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
    <div class="instruction-card-find instruction-card text-center">
      <h1>Find</h1>
      <p>Choose from various projects and activites others have created and join them!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="instruction-card-create instruction-card text-center">
      <h1>Create</h1>
      <p>Create your own projects or activites which others can then join!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="instruction-card-experience instruction-card text-center">
      <h1>Experience</h1>
      <p>Experience a new and better level of free time at University!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="section-explanation">
  <div class="container d-flex justify-content-center">
    <div class="explanation-card d-flex">
      <div class="explanation-card-text">
        <h1>A new world of things and people is here for you to discover!</h1>
        <p>- Do the activities you always wanted to try out!<br>
          - Start or join the projects that define you!<br>
          - Meet the people who you always wanted to meet<br>
          - Stop rewatching “The Office” for the 9th time!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="explanation-card-image"></div>
    </div>

  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="explanation-buttons">
      <button class="btn btn-light btn-big">
        More About Joind
      </button>
      <button class="btn btn-standard btn-primary btn-big">
        Join something!
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>




<h1>Home</h1>

